summary: VEHICLE OIL LINE EXPLODED. *MR  WHILE DRIVING DOWN THE HIGHWAY, THE ENGINE LIGHT CAME ON.  THE CONSUMER LIFTED THE HOOD AND VIEWED OIL EVERYWHERE.  THE SERVICE DEALER STATED THAT THE OIL LINE EXPLODED.  THE OIL LINE FROM THE OIL FILTER MOUNTED OFF THE ENGINE IN THE FRONT OF THE VEHICLE.   *SCC  *JB
